form texto_mes tables in_tab structure itcsy
                     out_tab structure itcsy.

  data: lv_fecha(10).
  data: lv_mes type t247-ltx.
  data: lv_date type datum.

* Leer el proveedor
  read table in_tab with key name = '&RFFBWE-BUDAT&'.
  lv_fecha = in_tab-value.
  concatenate lv_fecha+6(4) lv_fecha+3(2) lv_fecha(2) into lv_date.

  call function 'ISP_GET_MONTH_NAME'
    exporting
      date         = lv_date
      language     = sy-langu
      MONTH_NUMBER = '00'
    importing
*     LANGU_BACK         =
      longtext = lv_mes
*     SHORTTEXT          =
 EXCEPTIONS
     CALENDAR_ID        = 1
     DATE_ERROR         = 2
     NOT_FOUND          = 3
     WRONG_INPUT        = 4
     OTHERS   = 5
    .
  if sy-subrc <> 0.
* Implement suitable error handling here
  endif.

  read table out_tab index 1.
  move lv_mes to out_tab-value.
*  CONDENSE out_tab-value NO-GAPS.
  modify out_tab index 1.

endform. 
